node.text:
Do YOU think young people have the answers to make the #GlobalGoals a reality? 

94% of our #Kenya Hack participants said they did!  65 inspiring young people from Kenya, Tanzania and Uganda came together for the first of our #YOUTHPOWERHACKS in February, to generate fresh and innovative solutions for the Global Goals. 

Esmael – one of the participants – is passionate about working to ensure girls and women can exercise their power and rights. Have a listen to this voice note to learn more about his story and why he is taking part in the Youth Power Hacks. 

@restlessdevelopment 

#GenderEquality #Goal5
Very important conversation here👏 love to see this ❤️
